        </div>
      </div>

      <br \>

      <h2>Want to reach me?
        <small style="margin-left: 1.2em; font-size: 1.1rem;">Reach out to me on
          <u><a style="color:var(--link-color);" href="https://candost.blog/now/">Twitter @candosten</a></u>, on
          <u><a style="color:var(--link-color);" href="https://superpeer.com/candost/">Superpeer</a></u>, or via
          <u><a style="color:var(--link-color);" href="https://www.candostdagdeviren.com/contact/">contact form</a></u>.
        </small>
      </h2>
      <br \><br \>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
